snippet.title: Tim Dillard
snippet.description: Apartment Boy... We help our Clients for free when our Licensed Realtors find apartments in less time with less hassle in Austin, Dallas, Fort Worth, Houston and San Antonio.  We then give leveraged savings on things like monthly electric bills, movers, and much more to the clients we just helped for free and then we top it off with an Amazon Gift Card...  Finally, we also use funds generated from this effort to support poor and orphaned children through Rent-A-Life and World Vision.  Our "Apartment Boys" are a living, breathing brand come to life that show up at businesses to give them the Thumbs Up in a made for Social Media hyper event designed to bring attention to stores and businesses all over the state of Texas.  They are booking up for Ribbon Cuttings, Grand Openings, flash mob events and much more.  There is nothing like it.  Coming soon... the Apartment Girl.
